So a number of different ways that data scientists

00:27:24.500 --> 00:27:27.459
can use R and Python to deliver these wow results

00:27:27.459 --> 00:27:28.660
to the rest of the organization.

00:27:30.339 --> 00:27:32.099
For the DevOps and IT teams,

00:27:32.900 --> 00:27:34.660
