00:47:36.360 --> 00:47:37.560
or we can help you solve

00:47:37.560 --> 00:47:39.320
some of the challenges that come up.

00:47:39.320 --> 00:47:40.439
So I think that's kind of

00:47:40.439 --> 00:47:41.959
how I would end things there Lou

00:47:41.959 --> 00:47:43.399
is we'd love for you

00:47:43.399 --> 00:47:45.000
to dive into the resources

00:47:45.000 --> 00:47:46.439
dive into that community thread

00:47:47.080 --> 00:47:48.360
and then if you are

00:47:48.360 --> 00:47:49.719
encountering some of the challenges

00:47:49.719 --> 00:47:50.360
that we presented

00:47:50.360 --> 00:47:51.560
throughout this webinar

00:47:51.560 --> 00:47:52.760
feel free to reach out to us

00:47:52.760 --> 00:47:55.479
and we are happy to help you

00:47:55.479 --> 00:47:57.320
go through that path as well.

